sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    box rgb(200,220,255) Client Side
        actor User
        participant Browser
    end
    box rgb(220,255,220) Server Side
        participant API
        participant Auth
        participant DB
    end
    participant EmailSvc as Email Service

    User->>Browser: Submit login form
    activate Browser
    Browser->>+API: POST /auth/login
    API->>+Auth: validate(credentials)
    Auth->>+DB: SELECT user WHERE email=?
    DB-->>-Auth: user record
    alt Invalid credentials
        Auth-->>API: 401 Unauthorized
        API-->>Browser: 401 error
        Browser-->>User: Show error message
    else Valid credentials
        Auth-->>-API: JWT token
        API-)EmailSvc: Send login alert (async)
        Note right of EmailSvc: fire-and-forget
        API-->>-Browser: 200 + Set-Cookie
        deactivate Browser
        User->>Browser: Navigate to dashboard
        loop Poll for notifications
            Browser->>API: GET /notifications
            API-->>Browser: []
        end
    end
    Note over User,DB: Full auth flow complete
